     ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     QUICK REFERENCE for Kotlin:
       Only future:      dp.datePicker.minDate = today.timeInMillis
       Only next 20 days: dp.datePicker.minDate = today.timeInMillis
                          dp.datePicker.maxDate = maxDate.timeInMillis  (today+20)
